# Code Style and Documentation

We use the following features to review and edit our code style and documentation:

1. Reformat Code feature from Intellij (or shortcut ctrl+alt+l)

2. Inspect Code feature from Intellij

3. Check each warning/red sign for each file

4. Review each class to see if the documentation is clear and easier to understand by outer

5. Change/Add the commentary for each constant using in the program 